name: Antarctic Krill Oil 500mg Omega 3 Fatty Acid Supplement, MegaRed Extra Strength EPA & DHA Softgels (90cnt box), Antioxidant Astaxanthin, Heart Health Supplement With No Fish Oil Aftertaste
feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Krill is one of the world’s most abundant and sustainable organisms. MegaRed only sources krill from the Antarctic where krill is most abundant.,OMEGA 3 SUPPLEMENT: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil has been shown to significantly increase your omega 3 index in just 30 days. Supportive research has shown that consumption of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids may reduce the risk of coronary heart disease.,HEART HEALTH: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil supplements provide an optimal combination of omega-3 fatty acids and the powerful antioxidant astaxanthin to support heart health in a once daily softgel.,3X MORE PURE: MegaRed with PureTechTM is 3x MORE PURE than regular krill oil. Salts and other impurities are removed to provide the purest krill oil on the market.,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE and EASY ABSORPTION: Krill Oil is carried in a phospholipid form which is better absorbed by the human body and because it's krill oil as opposed to fish oil, MegaRed Krill Oil has no fishy aftertaste or odor.,These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

name: Barlean's Mango Peach Omega 3 Fish Oil Liquid Supplement with Vitamin D, 1080mg EPA & DHA Fatty Acid, Smoothie Flavored & Burpless for Brain, Joint, & Heart Health, 16 oz
feature_bullets: TASTE THE FRUIT, NOT THE FISH: Yummy fruity flavored fish oil with a creamy smoothie texture that both kids and adults love is the secret behind Barlean's Omega 3 fish oil liquid. 1080mg of EPA/DHA essential fatty acids per serving and 600 IUs (15 mcg) of vitamin D3 with no artificial flavors, colors or sweeteners. Our fish oil is dairy-free, sugar-free and non-GMO,3X BETTER ABSORPTION: We make Seriously Delicious Omega 3's with a proprietary process that turns wild caught, purified fish oil into a creamy and delicious omega 3 supplement that is highly absorbable and tested for mercury and other heavy metals. Because of our emulsified process Barlean's omega swirl is easier to digest, more absorbable, and no fish burps,FEEL YOUR BEST: Omega-3's are essential to a healthy diet, that's why Barlean's invented omega 3 liquid for kids and adults aimed at satisfying even the pickiest eaters. Each serving includes EPA/DHA to support brain, eye, heart, joint, & immune system health,SUGGESTED USE: Great straight off the spoon, drizzled over yogurt, or in oatmeal or smoothies. Adults & children ages 4 and up: 1 Tbsp daily. Keep out of reach of children and never give to pets. Refrigerate after opening,A NAME YOU KNOW AND TRUST: Barlean's has been selling premium dietary supplements since 1989, which is more than 30 years of helping people live their healthiest lives! We are passionate about healthy oils and helping people. Proudly made in the USA

name: BioEmblem Antarctic Krill Oil Supplement Turmeric Curcumin with Clinically Studied TurmiPure
feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL, RICH IN OMEGA-3s: BioEmblem's premium krill oil is sustainably harvested from the pristine waters of the Antarctic Ocean. Each 1000mg serving delivers 340mg of essential omega-3 fatty acids, 136mg of EPA, 64mg of DHA, along with phospholipids and astaxanthin.,SUPERIOR ABSORPTION FORM: Krill oil's phospholipid form of omega-3s can dissolve in water, allowing it to be better absorbed and more bioavailable compared to fish oils' triglycerides.* Krill oil also avoids the fishy aftertaste and odor associated with fish oils.,TurmiPure Gold - Clinically Studied For 24x Better Absorption: When it comes to turmeric's benefits, curcuminoid absorption is what matters the most. TurmiPure Gold is a patented turmeric extract made through a unique microemulsion process. This extract is clinically proven by studies to be 24x more bioavailable than standard turmeric curcumin extract with black pepper. Just 1 small capsule a day replaces 4 large standard turmeric supplement capsules.*,Scientifically Proven - Superior Bioavailability: Most turmeric curcumin formulas use large volume doses to make up for the fact that very little curcumin in them is actually absorbed into the blood. The curcumin in TurmiPure Gold extract on the other hand is much more highly absorbed. Human clinical trials have shown that just a small 300mg of TurmiPure Gold delivered more measurable curcuminoids into the bloodstream in 24 hours than other popular turmeric extract formulas in larger doses.*,Antioxidant Powerhouse & No Black Pepper: TurmiPure Gold contains powerful antioxidants that support the immune system, promote cognitive function and memory, support heart health, and promote healthy blood circulation – it provides whole-body health benefits. Because of its superior absorption, TurmiPure Gold extract doesn't need the black pepper or BioPerine that other turmeric capsules and curcumin supplements add.*

feature_bullets: WHY OMEGA-3s - Research shows that the essential fatty acids EPA & DHA in fish oil support heart, brain, eye & immune health. Omega-3s may also help support a healthy mood.,PERFECT FOR THOSE NEW TO FISH OIL - Nordic Naturals Omega-3 provides a generous serving of omega-3s in a great-tasting liquid, and meets the daily recommended dose suggested by the American Heart Association to support a healthy heart.,BETTER ABSORPTION, BETTER TASTE, NO FISHY BURPS - All of our omega-3 fish oils are offered in the triglyceride molecular form (the form naturally found in fish) for optimal absorption. Omega-3 has a great lemon taste.,PURITY GUARANTEED - Every batch of Nordic Naturals fish oil is crafted from fresh, wild-caught, omega-rich fish. We are committed to using only non-GMO, gluten- & dairy-free ingredients with no artificial colors, flavors, or preservatives.,ETHICAL INNOVATION - Nordic Naturals has always been at the forefront of sustainable & ethical practices in the natural products industry. Through science & innovation, we are committed to delivering safe, effective nutrients for optimal wellness.
